I"p<p>Just like, <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/feedforward-networks-approximate-functions">feedforward networks approximate functions</a>, recurrent networks approximate dynamical systems. The state of an RNN develops in <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/tense-logic-formalizes-time">time</a> across a trajectory based on the previous states.</p>
